This example gives an initial draft rendering of the ARC1 storage element, a
basic building block of the complete storage system[1] The rendering is based on the draft 28 of glue2 [2]. 


[1] http://svn.nordugrid.org/trac/nordugrid/browser/arc1/trunk/doc/storage_system/arc-storage-design.pdf
[2] http://forge.gridforum.org/sf/docman/do/downloadDocument/projects.glue-wg/docman.root.drafts/doc15023


